name: Chamber of Enigma, Cabinets Of Curiosities
description:
These was artworks presented in 2017 Osaka Unknown Asia. This was not presented like this, it was like a regular art fair. I edited it like this to fit the NFT space presentation.

I explored the theme of Cabinets of Curiosities here. We can talk about colonialism and post colonialism regarding this particular work, but I choose not to, because I am too lazy.
